    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272692</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>ちーす
雑貨屋「ほっかむり」っす</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey there, welcome to Bonnet.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272692</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>何がいるっすか～？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whattcha need?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272696</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>_shop_</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText/>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272700</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>あーっす</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Got it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272700</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>あ、「ありがとうございます」
ってことっす</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I mean...thanks and come again.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272704</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>この町はね、
昔エライなんとかっていう
学者さんがいたのよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A long time ago a really, uh...important
what's-their-name scholar visited this town.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272704</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>で、なんとかって理論を
提唱して、なんとかってのを
なくしたとかって……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>They proposed some kind of amazing thing
that was supposed to get rid of...something.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272708</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>この町出身のなんとかって学者さんの
エライ一言が世界を変えたの</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>In this very town, this what's-their-name scholar
shared a profound message that fundementally
changed the world as we know it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272708</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>スゴクない？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Pretty incredible, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272708</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>そして、そんな
スゴイこと覚えてないわたし、
もっとすごくない？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And the fact that I cannot remember a single
detail... doesn't that make this whole thing
even more incredible!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272712</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>いらっしゃい
雑貨屋「ベイビー」だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Welcome to the item shop Baby.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272712</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>何買うね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whatcha buying?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272716</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>_shop_</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText/>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272720</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>へい、まいど。
またおいで</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Thanks. Please come again.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272724</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>世界を救った&lt;Cless&gt;は
この町の誉れだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Cless&gt; brings this town great pride
for he deeds in saving the world.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272724</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>知っておるかの？
ユークリッド独立騎士団先代の
騎士団長ミゲールは&lt;Cless&gt;の父だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Did you know that &lt;Cless&gt;'s father,
Miguel, was the former captain of 
Euclid's Independent Order of Knights?</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Use the Aselia Wiki Translation for 独立騎士団 </Notes>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272728</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Cless&gt;はわしらが町が
育てたといっても
過言ではない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The people of this place raised
&lt;Cless&gt; and that is no exaggeration.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272728</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>過言ではない、
過言ではないぞ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No exaggeration, I tell you.
None whatsoever!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272732</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>法術はもともとこの町を発祥とし
世界に広まった技術なのじゃ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Magic, as the world knows it,
started here in this town.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272732</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>つまりこの町は
すべての法術師誕生の地とも
言えるじゃろう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>In other words, you could see that
this town is the birthplace of all
mages, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272736</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mint&gt;はわしらが町が
育てたといっても
過言ではない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It would be no exaggeration to say that
this place birthed &lt;Mint&gt;, you know.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>The phraseology is the same for each character, but I wrote it in a way that was unique to the preceeding sentences.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272736</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>過言ではない、
過言ではないぞ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No exaggeration, I tell you.
None whatsoever!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272740</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Klarth&gt;博士の研究は
このユークリッドから
始まったのじゃ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Did you know that Professor &lt;Klarth&gt;'s 
research began here in Euclid?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272740</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>召喚術研究から
「魔科学廃絶論」……
すべてこの町で考えられたのじゃ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>From summoning research to the
"Magitech Abolition Theory"...
all of it was conceived here.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>魔科学 translated to magitech as that is what it was called in Phantasia.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272744</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Klarth&gt;はわしらが町が
育てたといっても
過言ではない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It is no exaggeration to say that
this place was instrumental to
Professor &lt;Klarth&gt;'s research.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>The phraseology is the same for each character, but I wrote it in a way that was unique to the preceeding sentences.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272744</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>過言ではない、
過言ではないぞ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No exaggeration, I tell you.
None whatsoever!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272748</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>はいはい、
雑貨屋「ほっかむり」よん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This is the item store Bonnet.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272748</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>なんかほしいもんあったら
持ってって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Grab anything that suits your fancy.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272752</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>_shop_</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText/>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272756</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>持ってってもいいけど
お金は置いてってね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>When I said grab anything, you do
know you still have to pay, yeah?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>30</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272760</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>グミは買った……
ライフボトルも……
後は武器屋行って……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Gel, check. Life bottle, check.
All that is left is the weapon shop...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>31</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272760</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>あ、僕、騎士なんだ。
今日は非番なんだけど。
休みの日はショッピングだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This knight is off duty today.
It's my day off and is the only
time I can get my shopping done.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>31</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272764</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>僕は
ユークリッド黒鎧騎士団の
騎士だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I have the honor to serve as a member
of the Order of the Black Knights.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>黒鎧騎士団 = Order of the Black Knights per Aselia Wiki</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>33</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272764</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>誉れ高き黒鎧に誓い
今日もこの国の平和を
双肩に担う！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>By wearing this black armor, 
we are duty bound to bring peace
to the nation each and every day!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>33</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272764</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>でも、今日は非番……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Just not today, because
it's my day off...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>33</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272768</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>グミは……うーん、
足りない……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Gel... Hmm,
I don't have enough...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>36</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272768</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>僕は騎士団の騎士なんだが
安月給でね、アップルグミも
買えないありさまさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm a knight of the order, but the
wages are so low... I can't even
afford to buy an Apple Gel.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>36</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272772</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>アップルグミが買えないと
他の何も買えない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If I cannot even afford an Apple Gel,
what is there that I can even buy?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>38</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272772</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>後は騎士団の支給品で
しのぐしかないか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I guess I have no other option than to
rely on the provisions provided by the order...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>38</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272776</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>騎士ってもっと評価されても
いい仕事だと思うんだけど……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Us knights deserve to be valued more...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>40</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272776</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>今のこの国じゃ
評判はいまひとつ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We do not have the best reputation currently.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>40</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272776</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>もう騎士団、辞めようかな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Maybe I should just leave...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>40</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272780</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>もう騎士とか
今は流行りじゃないんだよな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Knights are no longer really needed.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>43</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272780</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>これからは知恵でもって
世界を守る時代なのかもね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Perhaps we've entered into an age where
the world is protected by wisdom, not knights.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>43</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
